                        <interp inst="t18431023-name-1529" type="given" value="WILLIAM"></interp>WILLIAM FORDHAM</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">policeman.</hi>) I observed the window of West's house about seven o'clock in the morning—it had been forced open by some instru<lb></lb>ment—I apprehended Nowland,</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18431023-name-1530" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18431023-name-1530" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
