                        <interp inst="t18431023-name-1530" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>JOHN WRIGHT</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">policeman.</hi>) I took Lucas, with the counterpane on his head, about five minutes to seven o'clock—Nowland was taken first, but they had separated.</p>
